OL,3,CNational Rail 'warned' about repairs
OL,4,Cbefore pensioner struck by train
OL,6,FThe Rail Accident Investigation Branch
OL,7,F(RAIB) is now looking into how the
OL,8,Fcollision happened.
OL,10,FPeople in Pewsey say her death was
OL,11,Fpreventable. Shirley normally used a
OL,12,Fbridge but it had been closed by
OL,13,FNetwork Rail and was awaiting
OL,14,Freplacement.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
