OL,3,CNational Rail 'warned' about repairs
OL,4,Cbefore pensioner struck by train
OL,6,FLiz Donaldson, Shirley's friend, said:
OL,7,F"I knew Shirley through dog walking.
OL,8,FShe had a lovely lab, very friendly,
OL,9,Fuse to liked my lab. She was a very
OL,10,Fnice lady, rather quiet, lived here
OL,11,Ffor a long, long time. Part of the dog
OL,12,Fwalking community."
OL,14,FResidents say they warned National
OL,15,FRail several times and the local MP
OL,16,FDanny Kruger says it's such a simple
OL,17,Fstructure it would be an easy job to
OL,18,Freplace it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
