OL,3,CNational Rail 'warned' about repairs
OL,4,Cbefore pensioner struck by train
OL,6,FDanny Kruger, Conservative MP for East
OL,7,FWiltshire, said: "A lady has died,
OL,8,Fmuch-loved neighbour of people here
OL,9,Fand the tragedy was this was warned
OL,10,Fof. People were writing in saying 'it
OL,11,Fis dangerous'.
OL,13,F"You have trains travelling nearly 100
OL,14,Fmiles an hour around a corner toward a
OL,15,Flevel crossing. This lady clearly
OL,16,Fdidn't have enough time to get across
OL,17,Fwhen that train hit and this is
OL,18,Fsomething that people had been raising.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
