OL,3,CNational Rail 'warned' about repairs
OL,4,Cbefore pensioner struck by train
OL,6,F"So there is real concern, some anger,
OL,7,Fat the length of time it's taken to
OL,8,Ffix this, the failure of Network Rail
OL,9,Fto communicate properly. "
OL,11,FThe old bridge will now be replaced in
OL,12,FJune.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for Network Rail said
OL,15,Ftheir thoughts remain with everybody
OL,16,Faffected by Shirley's death. They
OL,17,Fadded they welcome the review by the
OL,18,FRAIB and that they're holding their
OL,19,Fown internal review as well.
